-- Esoteric North Star Seven-Star Pendant
INSERT INTO products (id, name, slug, description, price, salePrice, categoryId, stock, status, blessingLocation, blessingMaster, createdAt, updatedAt)
VALUES (510055, 'Esoteric North Star Seven-Star Pendant', 'esoteric-north-star-seven-star-pendant', 'Across ancient civilizations, the Big Dipper (北斗七星) was more than a constellation — it was revered as a symbol of "universal order," a celestial compass for navigation, and a protective sigil for travelers on both physical and spiritual journeys. In Eastern esoteric traditions, the Seven-Star Array is invoked for protection, destiny alignment, and connection to cosmic forces. This pendant carries the weight of that legacy, enhanced by a time-honored ceremonial process that infuses it with the Seven-Star Array''s inherent energetic properties. The innovative dual-layer rotating design (can rotate 360 degrees) isn''t just aesthetic: it mirrors the Big Dipper''s eternal movement across the heavens, acting as a physical reminder to "sync" with the universe''s supportive currents. The front displays the seven stars in their sacred configuration, while the reverse features the Eight Trigrams (八卦) representing the fundamental forces of existence. Crafted with precision (pendant diameter: approx. 35.5mm, height: approx. 40.5mm, chain length: approx. 60mm), this piece combines ancient symbolism with contemporary craftsmanship. Worn close to the body, it is said to ward off unbalanced energies, amplify inner clarity and purpose (tied to the Big Dipper''s "guidance" legacy), and serve as a tangible link to the cosmos'' quiet, protective power. For those who seek alignment with celestial wisdom and cosmic protection.', 45.0, 55.0, 8, 999, 'published', '五台山', '五台山高僧', NOW(), NOW());

